text:
‚ÄúApan ek doosre ke liye bade memoir likh rahe hai kya?‚Äù - Perfectly sums up our friendship. Pehle din ke chutiya discussion se start hui ye dosti, aaj tak chutiya discussion hi jhel rahi hai. Bahut hi zyada memories hai inn kuch shabdo mai bayan karne ke liye, isiliye jo yaad aa raha hai likh de raha hu. I know you‚Äôll understand xD 

Kaafi ups and downs rahe hai yaar meri life mai, chahe scenarios and problems badalti rahi ho, tu constant support tha life mai and I feel that I have not thanked you enough for that. I will still not do it because tujhpe aati to mai bhi karta na bro xD. Chahe mere saare elections mai mere saath ghumna ho, meri acads mai jitna ho sake utni help karna ho, meri bandiyo ko RR sunna ho, ya infinite chutiya baate discuss karni ho, you have always been there, Bhatia. I guess ye kehna galat nahi hoga ki apan vo college mai jo best friend dhoondne aaye the, vo dhoond liya tha. However, teri relationship problems beech mai aa jaati hai xD 

Main reason nahi hu teri zindagi mai chutiyappo ka bc, at least 51% share usmain tera hi hai. Chahe jo bhi path apan dono ne choose kiya hai, teri respect to hamesha hi karunga mai bro, aakhir group ka ‚Äúdependable‚Äù banda jo hai tu xD. Yes, I just implied that we have a group. Aakhir last mai jaate jaate ek actual gehrai wala group mil hi gaya. 

Vaise to apan emotional hote nahi hai usually, but ek baar to banta hai I guess. 

Chalo fir, milte rehna? Milenge hi bro, teri shaadi mai to aaunga hi at least. Fir saath mai judge bhi to karenge teri wali ko :) 

Thanks for everything, bro.
author: Nikunj  Kothari

text:

Hope that we meet again. Cheers!

text:
‚ÄúPune mai sirf ek taraf incline hai bro, paani hi nahi bharta hai.‚Äù - still being the best reason why Pune is the best. First week se leke kal phone pe baat karne tak, bahut yaadein bana li hai bro apan ne. Mai tujhse sabse pehle impress tab hua tha jab tune baap wing meet mai 5 porn stars ke naam bata diya fatafat and fir tujhe DoPA banaya gaya tha. 
Bahut hi unconventional thinking hai teri bro, from liking Hitler‚Äôs ideology to thinking about converting to DD for Gensec. Still, aisi soch ke saath bhi amazingly chappu hai tu. Mad respect for how you lived your journey at IITK, bro. You truly deserve that award.  
I still remember how you conned me into accepting that ITC internship but that honestly turned out to be one of the best decisions of my life (I guess kuch aisi cheezein to maine bhi kari hai tere saath, so we are balanced xD). 
Tere liye bada memoir likhne ki zaroorat nahi hai kyuki Mumbai main milte hi rahenge but still writing it because 20 years down the line jab tu ye yearbook dekhe aur apne marathi bachcho ko padhaye, toh usmai mai bhi aau xD 

It has been a great journey dude, thank you for everything.

text:
‚ÄúTu bhi Kothari? Mai bhi Kothari.‚Äù - Aakhir bar to bada high set kardiya apan ne. Chahe first year se tujhse bandiyo aur intern ka gyaan lene se, 1 hafte pehle stock market ka gyaan lene tak, tu hamesha hi chaapta raha hai bro. 

Tere saath high ya bhand ya high hona hi reh gaya yaar, kabhi maze karenge saath mai pakka se. I am sure tu life mai bahut bada aadmi banega bro, bhul mat jaana. Also, mai ameer nahi hu (at least abhi to xD).  

Kuch zyada shabd nahi aa rahe hai yaar abhi dhyan mai, but dil main bahut emotions hai. 

Kabhi milenge jab tu India aayega, bas yaad rakhna.

Although the course was left off-way (half-way) due to covid, we still managed to read the novel Hotel Silence by Au√∞ur Ava √ìlafsd√≥ttir and write a term paper. Our paths might be very different now.  Hope that we will connect sometime in the future to relive the TRC chapter.  All the best for your future endeavors.
author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Jaya,

You were one among the two "Jaya"s that I knew at IIT K. The other one is Jaya Srivastava from Y18.  I can see that you were a good student guide of Jaya Srivastava who also joined the E club one year after you.  

Opting for a double major in electrical was a good decision by you.  Hope that you will contact me again during the pre-registration for next semester. I will be happy to help you in deciding the elective courses.  

All the best for your future endeavors.
author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Madhur,

We knew each other through SnT council. I had heard a lot about you from Jay.  We interacted mostly in the SnT council meets in Senate Hall. I recall that you had participated in the Electrowiz competition conducted by Eclub in senate hall. Your team was among the top-performing teams (mostly because many of the questions that I had set were from our common EE courses). Although we didn't collaborate much over any project, it was fun to jointly organize many events for SnT council.  I wish that we would have collaborated more with the Robo club.

Besides SnT council, we did our EMEC lab of EE381 together. In 8th sem, we also did Prof. AKJ's estimation and detection course together. Our areas of interest may be quite different now. Hope that our paths may cross sometime in the future. All the best for your future endeavors.
author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Naishadh,

Our interaction has been mostly limited to our second-year journey in ERA.  You were among the most hardworking members of our team.  Our entire third and fourth sem were entirely devoted to ERA.  We used to discuss the updates in the challenge even during EE250, EE210 lectures. We had jointly explored the area of reinforcement learning (although we did not use RL in the final submission).  We also shared many jokes together. Do you remember my vision for "Umbrella Organization"?

I was expecting you to apply for team-head in third year.  Anyways, neither of us pursued robotics after the third year. Our areas of interest are quite different now. Hope that you will stay in touch.  All the best for your future endeavors.
author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Soumya, 

I am glad that I met you at IIT K in our second year.  We have been through several ups and downs together (especially third sem and fourth sem).  We connected first time through Eclub.  Remember the time when ERA was being founded. Most of our time together in second year was spent in Prof Behera's lab, EClub and later at Hall 12 ERA room / Suraj's room.

We had also collaborated in TIIDC. You had accompanied me in finding a faculty mentor the day before deadline. The funniest part of TIIDC was recording the video.  You have supported me in all of my crazy ventures. 

The one unique thing that you taught me was sending GIFs on Facebook messenger. Our chat is full of GIFs.

You really manage your time well. You took several leadership roles simultaneously in SnT council. You led several problem statements
author: Nitish Vikas Deshpande

text:
Hi Tarish,

You are among the one at IIT K whom I know the longest.  We know each other since class 8. We were together for the Young Scientist exam coaching class by Kotwal ma'am. After that, we joined Vidyalankar for Physics Olympiad classes.  Are you in touch with our mutual friends from Vidyalankar? 

You were the coordinator of the coolest club in SnT council. I remember the night that I spent in Astro club when collaborating for a SnT council proposal.
Thanks for allowing Eclub to conduct one of our secys meets at Astro club.
I wish that I could have spent more time at Astro Club.

It is great that you pursued your liking towards Physics and Astronomy at IIT K. I recall that you had medals in Astronomy Olympiads before joining college. Although I don't know much about astronomy, radio astronomy sounds cool as it has a bit of intersection with electrical engineering. I recall that you too, had collaborated with the Microwave lab in EE for one of your projects. 

Physics and electrical engineering have a good amount of intersection. Hopefully, our paths might cross again in the future.

If you are in Thane, we might meet up sometime.

All the best for your future endeavors.

author: Palak  Agrawal

text:
Aaj likhne ka kaafi mood bana hai, to thoda lamba or senti jaayega, padhke to tune khush hi hona hai madarchod, tu hi bolti hai naa jyada expressive nahi hu me, pehli or aakhiri baar express kr rhi, to khush ho jaana pdhke, iske baad nhi hone waala ye. One of the best things jo IITK ne mjhe diya hai wo tu hai (sounding like Nareda I know, but chill hai). Yaad hoga tjhe kaisi masoom si, bholi bhaali aayi thi me, mjhe jo itna frank kiya hai logo se, sikhaya ki dost duniya itni achi nhi hai jitni tum samajhti ho, duniya madarchod hai. Har ek cheez me mjhe support kiya, rules todhne sikhaye (sbse epic ESC201 tha), mere itne jyada saare randi rone sune har time, gaaliyan bhi di hai sunne ke baad, but har cheez ka solution nikal jaata tha yrr tjhse baat krke. Ek point tha meri har problem ka solution tu thi, fir ek point aaya (pata hi hoga kyu aaya), jab , meri sbse badi problem hi tu thi. Behenchod, agar kisi insaan ki wajah se me zindagi me kabhi royi hungi naa to wo tu hai. Behechod, bolti hai ki JD or tum ekdum similar ho, to ye nhi samajh aaya tjhe ki wo rota hai itna, to ho sakta hai me bhi roti hu. Mtlb me close nhi hoti logon se jyada, pata hi hai tjhe, but pata nhi terese hu. Wahan Shimla me literally meri feelings ye thi ki yaar sahi me bohot sahi tha pehle ki kisise bhi close nhi thi, kyuki end me to sbko chhodna hi hota hai, ye bhi chhod hi di naa (firse Nareda waali feel). But thike, mtlb mjhe pata hai me tere liye kaafi important hu, but bc banda aane ke baad sab badal jaate hai, tum bhi koi exception nhi thi. Or agar campus me mjhe sbse jyada nafrat ek insaan se hai to wo hai JD, but baat ye hai ki uski jyada koi glti nhi hai usme. Shimla waali trip bohot hi jyada bekaar thi, wahan pe pata nhi hoga 2 raat me bhi kaafi royi thi, but hamesha ki tarah tu thi nhi sambhalne ko, kyuki pati bhi tha naa tumhare paas to, or fir uske baad jab time bacha to tumne Karan ko pakad liya, jisse hume realise hua ki tumhare liye life me aage badhna or doosre log dhoondna bohot aasan hai (another instance jab tune abhi campus me kaha tha ki me nhi aa rhi hall, mjhe hall-9 me patte khelne me bohot majja aa rha hai), but JD or mere jaise logo ke liye nhi hai, yaad rakhna isse. Khair, dost shukriya humare jeevan me aane ke liye, humko sudharne ke liye, Tindal jaise logon ko judge krne me humari help krne ke liye, or hume humare ye upar likhe hue jaise faaltu ke randi rone sunke unko suljhaane ke liye. Me jaanti hu bohot saare logon ko campus me, but dil ka connect sirf tere saath hai, chuhiya, Thanya kisike saath nhi hai. Itni connected bachpan se aaj tak apne gharwaalo ke alawa shayad nhi hongi kisise bhi. Lekin behenchod isiliye connect nhi hoti me, kyuki fir uss insaan se related faaltu ki baaton pe bohot jyada sochne lag jaati hu me, or ye khaaali hone ka asar nhi hai agar tjhe wo lag raha hai to. Agar me bohot jyada hi busy hoti naa to bhi mjhe tere ye last 1 mahine ke ignorance se shayad utna hi farak padta. Bas bhadas thi nikaal di, feel mat krna jyada warna ro dogi. Achi insaan ho yrr tum, bas exclusice raho humare liye, sbke paas jaa jaake unki dikkatein naa suljhaya karo, I feel jealous (ye nhi btaya maine shayad tjhe kabhi pehle). PLease meri life se jaana mat kabhi bhi. Baaki to me nhi jaane dungi, bas JD ki baat aati hai to me fir piche ho jaati hu. Wahan tjhe hi sambhalna pdega. BC pdhte pdhte gaaliyan de rhi hogi ki ek rone waala kam tha kya jo isne bhi shuru kr diye, but thike mummy se nhi royenge to kisse royenge, or hum thodi roj roj rote hai. 

BC bas visible mat krna isko, acha sa gaaliyon bhara likhenge tumhara visible karane le liye.
author: Palak  Agrawal

author: Palak  Agrawal

text:
PR calling Festi!!
Yaar teri first memory naa 1st year ki hai, jab tu Katiyar ke liye birthday card banane GH ayaa tha, lol (Am I allowed to openly say this?). Hamesha ye discussion kaafi hota tha humara ki kaafi similar ho tum dono, literal bhai lagte ho. 
Anyway, uske baad Antaragni'19 ke baad ig diwali ke baad call aata hai tera, bro milna hai kuch gadbad ho gyi. BC bhand hoke chhoti ko bata diya tha tune, meri fati nhi thi, but jis tareeke se tu express kr rha tha, aisa lag rha tha ki fatni chahiye. Uske baad to yrr fir CORE TEAM, alag feels, alag expectations, or kaafi jyada enthu. Enthu to ussi se yaad aata hai jo "KAIROS" naam pe kitna jyada discussion hua tha, lol. But, ek point aane ke baad, enthu kaafi down ho gaya tha. Tune or Shrey ne hi milke sambhala tha poora, placements ke baad sbko jinda kiya, or fir karali BC (wo feel nhi hai, but apni Antargni thi yrr). Bohot jyada miss kiya maine, jo hall-12 me saath milke kaam or bakchodi ki hai tum logo ne (photos or videos aa rhi thi mere paas regularly), or jo final night bhand hue ho tum log. Goa trip jldi plan karo yrr, saath me bhand hona hai BC (OAT ki tarah nhi hopefully).  Dukh kaafi raehga on-ground Antaragni naa hone ka, jitna expected tha utni bond nhi ho paayi me team me, but at the end kya hi kar sakte hai.  Khair kaafi BT hai meri udhar, Tindal ke saamne nahi nikali kabhi, tere saamne pata nhi kyu nikal rhi. Anyways, umeed hai Goa me jld hi milenge. Tab tak Take Care, or apna enthu or feel humesha aisi hi rakhna!!

text:
Hi Pandey..hope u have moved on by now. I didn‚Äôt want to write anything about you after what you have doneüò†(those who know, know it), but tum dil k kafi achhe aadmi ho‚ù§Ô∏è. Also, I know that it was your last possible chance, so I forgive you. I can write a whole page on this topic..you know that...but i will maintain the dignity of memoir and epsilon amount of  your ijjat. 
We didn‚Äôt talk even once during our 1st year, cause you were maggu at that time...baat krne  k liye kha hi time tha tere pas...and at that time, mere ko ye bilkul ye nhi lga ki we will become such a good friend. From the time I know you, you were the most chillest person of our wing, and ofc Chapu. Do u remember, tumhare pas kafi stories hoti thi , and u needed someone to spill it out. And then you come to most vella guy of the wing, who had always time for others (ofc it was me). That was the time when we got along and the strength of our friendship increased, if u remember. I really enjoyed those stories man (just say thanks from my side to the main storyteller). do u remember, ek din mera laptop aur notebook sb le liye the..just bcz i was not ready to listen to your stories...agle subah quiz thi...b**k aise harkate mt kiya kro, nhi to koi suplex deke chala jayega.I know i hit u once, i‚Äôm really sorry for this...but kya mja aaya tha yar...aisa lga i‚Äôm in wwe ring, and i‚Äôm giving you superman punch. Even after this, we are such a good friend. But i have to ask you a question. Why you always betray me??chahe wo fluid mechanics ki endsem ho ya placement session ho...why??? jaise bhi ho bhai...but tum dil k kafi achhe ho...and it‚Äôs very difficult to find people with a good heart...mai khud ko kafi lucky manta hu ki i got friends like you...playing full night badminton and volleyball...wo bhi kya din the..i really miss those days yar...and yes we haven‚Äôt gone to any trip together, but next time be ready...to sponsor my trip!üòç(JPMC k itne paise ka kya krega). So, thank you for making my life at campus more beautiful and memorable bhai. There is a quote ‚ÄúHope for the best, but be prepared for the worst‚Äù. ‚ÄòWorst‚Äô to tumhare sath ho hi chuka hai, now its time for the best. So, All the best for your future ahead. Bhut paise kamao...Be Rich...Ambani is not that far!
P.S. - You deserve someone better!
author: Mukesh  Kumar

text:
Hello Anshu (pet name revealed)..
Bhai, I just can‚Äôt imagine it‚Äôs been 7 years of friendship..and I wish ki it remains forever‚ù§Ô∏è. It is very difficult for any friendship to go so long. We both are very thankful to god that everything happened in our favour. I came to know you during our JEE preparations at FIITJEE. Initially I thought...ya, seems like a nice guy...started talking...and eventually became good friends while helping each other in solving fiitjee booklets. U remember anshu? that fight between us...MTH publication k book ko leke...i refused to give it to you, and u stopped talking to me...was kidding manüòÇ...and then we became very good friends. This made me realise ki with whoever i had a little nok jhok , they became very good friends of mine (kyo pandey aur piyush üòÇ). We got so lucky bhai‚Ä¶.same batch at FIITJEE, both repeated for JEE, again got in the same institute and batch(Parth Ranker ROCKS(rock emoji)), and fortunately got in the same college and even the same hall bhaiüíó...everything happened in favor of our friendship. And I feel very lucky that you are one of my friends, and trust me, you have a very special place in my lifeü§ó. I mean it needs a lot of effort to maintain any type of relationship, and I respect you a lot for all your efforts to keep our friendship going. 
This whole memoir would be like green trees but with no fruits if I don‚Äôt talk about our college life. You made these whole four years of college life really awesome by showing us your writing skill. Bhai mera SHAYAR..kasam se yar...kya likhte ho bhai..ekdum gaddar...I had only listend earlier ki ‚ÄúPYAR ME LOG SHAYAR BN JATE HAI‚Äù, but you made me believe it. Here is a two-liner that came in my mind spontaneously, hope u like it:
Ek tum aur tera adhoora pyar, i wish ki it happens bar bar;
You might not want it to happen again, but trust me, this will be the reason for your name and fame!
I just can‚Äôt wait to see you on youtube and your book to be a bestseller in India...macha dena bhai! 
And yes, thank you for being there whenever I needed someone. Whenever I was in a confusion for choosing or doing something or not, you were the first person who I went to. And, ofc how can we both forget that traumatic period of my lifeüò¢...man i just can‚Äôt tell how i would have been if u were not there. I am really really thankful to you bhai. And thanks to you for making me start all the nashe thingsüòú...it really feels amazing. Kuchh nashe bache hai, but i know ki tu uski bhi aadat lgwa dega. But, how could I forget that Nainital trip man. Bhai, mai maut ko takk se choo k wapas aa gya tha...it was scary..but i really enjoyed it man. The funniest trip was our regular Patna trip. Sutta fukna at every Patna trip. Jb bhi tum patna aate the, ek lambi list hoti thi tumhare pas, of all the street-food and their locations.Jha bhi jao, ‚Äòpaisa wasool‚Äô ki responsibility tum lete the. Bhai, to ek din bhukha aata tha, paisa wasool krne k liye. and ghar jakar pta chlta tha ki you have gained 5 kgs of weight...i mean are you for real??? And itne khane wale bnde ko achanak se diet follow krna, i can‚Äôt believe my eyes. Jo bhi ho, you are following it strictly, and yes huge respect for this. Aur bhai, wo 85 kg wali bet ko jyada serious mt le yar, gareeb aadmi ko jeene nhi doge kyaüòÇ. The most hilarious and memorable trip to Patna was of course Jan‚Äô21. First of all, you should thank me for making you lose your weights, and saving your auto ka kirayaüòú. We did so much kand bhai...you know that! 
Last but not the least, I wish you very very good luck for your great journey ahead. I hope you fulfill all your dreams, and most importantly follow your diet, cause the ‚ÄòBET‚Äô is still ON.
Love you 3000xüíìüíì
P.S.- tujhe kya, phatna hoga to phat jaunga;
	Apne baap ka khata hu, nikal warna yhi utha k patak dunga!

yaad hai mujhe sabse pehle tu kaise mila tha.. mai , tushar aur aanshul apne room me the tab tu aur ip(saanp) aaya aur tum dono aake bade ajeeb tarike se baat kiye humse. Actually ajeeb tab laga q ki tab bohot gaaliya deke baat kar rhe the tum logüòÇüòÇ abhi yaad karta hu toh lagta hai normal toh thaüòÇüòÇ. Apan ek sath freshers mein dance kiye lekin tab nhi jaante the... asli janne lage jab 2nd year start hua tab. tere room me aana jaana start hua. jab bhi aata tha sota rehta tha aur darr k uth jaata tha. Aur fir bolta tha "areee yaar mai so gya padhna tha mujheü§£ü§£". wo bhi kya din the. Asli maza tab aana start hua jab avi tu aur mai milke chize karna start kar diye. jaise bahar jaana . bakchodi karna., piza hut toh bhai bhai yaad hi rahega. Roshan se bhi mila tere karan. Aur wo tere birthday wali raat bhai maza aa gya tha. bancho meri lene lag gye the sabüòÅüòÅ. bhai wo plane banani wali lab jisme jaate the ..tu kaam kart tha aur hum kitne bakchodi karte the. kitne din exam k pehle sath me padheüòâ(ghanta padhe). Mirzapur sath me dekha tha jisme sadke patli patli thiü§£ü§£.     Baaki sab badhiya tha yaar bas last mein thodi chize bigad gyi..lekin mujhe pata hai q hui ... hall change nhi hona chahiye tha yaar. same hall mein rehte na toh mast hota. baaki yaar mai yahi boulnga ki wo time bhool jaao.  Tere sath trip pe jaana reh hi gya..koi nhi meri job lagte hi jayenge aur tu bhi IAS ban jayega tab tak. fir foreign ki trip karengeüòçüòç. tu toh mujhe har baar yaad karega jab "ba ko va pronunce karegaü§£ü§£" Baaki yahi bolunga thanks bhai.. in 4 saalo me anginat lamhe sath mein bitaye and mai hamesha yaad karunke khush hounga (last me 1-2 assu bhi niklenge but khushi kü•∫) . milte hai jald hi.

text:
Yaar vakul ab kya likhu mein. Tu ek aisa banda hai jiske sath mujhe lagta hai memories kam bani. Abhi jab apan bichad gye to mai sochta hu ki yaar kaash aur time sath mein hota aur time chahiye tha apna sath mein. Past mein jaake mai sochta hu toh mujhe samaz aaya ki aisa q hua. Jab tu, tushar aur anshul k sath rehne laga tab mai dance mein busy tha aur apna time sync nhi ho paaya. Kaash tu thoda pehle aaataüò≠üò≠...kaash. Par chalo ab jo bhi memories hai use hi yaad karte hai. Manali trip toh puri college life mein sabse badhiya chiz thi. Aur waha hi tere sath pehli baar kch genuine yaade baniüòÇüòÇ. Kitne maze kiye yaar trip pe, kaash ek aur trip ho jaatiüò•.....kaash. Trip pe tu hamesha udaas rehta tha tu qki tujhe lagta tha ki ulti ho jayegiü§£ü§£.  jab Kunal ultiya karne laga tab tu fence k bahar jaake khada ho gya wo kitna funny thaü§£ü§£. Fir tu mai aur baba ek hi tent mein soye the. Aur maza aaya tha jab paragliding k liye jaa rhe the tab mai tujhe bol rha tha ki mai bhi nhi karunga toh tu bolne laga ki haan apan dono nhi karenge. lekin baadme kar hi liya sabneüòÇ. Chalo Trip kahatm hui. Ab baat karte hai aakhri 2 mahine jo sath mein the. Yaar time kitne jaldi nikal gya. Kaash aur time milta sath mein.....kaaash. Wo time best tha yaar jo bhi mila hame sath mein tum teeno k sath jo bhi maze kiye maza aagya. Bhalehi tum logo ne mere bina bhi maze kar liye bohot lekin kya karta padhna bhi thana mujhe toh mai hamesha sath nhi reh paayaüò•(mai hamesha regret karunga ye baat). Ek din pehle jo show chalaya tune wo bhi mujhe yaad rahegaüòÇ. Tujhe high dekh k maine bhi socha hai ki jab job lag jayegi tab mai bhi apna show chalaunga ek baar tohüòÇ.  
Aakhri mein yahi kahunga ki regret toh hai par khushi bhi hai ki kam hi sahi bohot achha time spend kiya tere sath. Dance video bhi toh banna hai.üòÇ...I will miss you my boiiü•∞ü•∞.
author: Parag Nandaram Sonkusare

text:
It‚Äôs really hard to express your simplicity and sweetness in words - easily one of the nicest person I know o:)Have seen you inside out (You know what I mean :P)..shouldn‚Äôt go into details on public records. Some things about you really intrigue me - how can someone play all day long (you should be the poster boy of Glucon-D) and have so much organised hostel room (Dude, really WTF!, they are not supposed to be organised in the first place :-)). 
It was a pleasure being your script-writer from Nishika in fresher to Minki in senior year...chutiya tmhara kata...but dukh hmko bhi hua ;)...I guess they didn‚Äôt know you have 6-pack abs, a good job and a kind soul (Khud so jaayenge usko‚Ä¶..)..oh that qualifies you for marriage (already late by Rajasthani standards xD).. can wait to share your rangeen hostel kisse with bhabhi-sa (it‚Äôs time to forget Kristen Stewart).
Your room has always been our backchodi adda...your Gurgaon flat will be one too :) You are better than a bank when it comes to safeguarding money but you used to steal my roomie and his shipment..very bad! ;) Just a friendly reminder - I play better badminton and mini-militia than you. Period. Most probably you would agree, if not, I do have ice cream.
I have got your back just like that Antaragni night dare. Have roamed around a lot together, still, a lot left to explore.  It would be near impossible for someone to know you and not like you for the person you are. Thanks for always being there except PHY103 endsem...hahaha!!. Love you, bro! M just a call away! All the best! A very bright future awaits!
P.S - Is sem to firse dassa aarha hoga !?

text:
You were a hard nut, thankfully I had Meena to help me crack you up. You are a bit moody and sometimes seriously mess up. Hopefully, you remember a few quarrels we had but it turned out fine in the end. Having DOPA as roommate has its own perk and I must say, you have a very well-curated collection :P got a lot of exposure from you -from CCD‚Äôs devils own to good English music, from GOT to the vixen, and many more.

Your attention to minute and keen sense of design is remarkable. Most people here do things that will either fetch good grades or land them a fat job. In that sense, you were very different. Though sometimes overdone, I like your ‚ÄòDoing only things I like‚Äô attitude i.e I remember you watching ‚ÄòThe Office‚Äô instead of studying for Endsem but at the same time putting extra hours to learn Sanskrit and philosophy! 

Do u remember our intense philosophical discussions especially in CCD and those late-night walks afterwards (Wo Jaan Jaan kehke jaan le gye) ?..good old days!  Intelligent to ho hi sir aap bs put your ass to work! All the best! Happy researching! 
B-319 ka tempo high hai!

text:
I don't know you
Nor you me

I am just chilling
and picking random names
and writing this poem
to memoir these beautiful times

we wrote an exam
the best there is
and spent our pass
of these four years

we fought for things
we read for hours
we played and made friends
this was best time of ours

I don't know you 
Nor you me

- A random y17

text:
Abe mujhe nahi laga tha tere liye bhi memoir likhna hai.. Ek tu hi hai jiske liye likhna sabse mushkil hoga.. Jo bhi likhu kam hai aur kuch na kuch reh jaega.. Sabse pehle toh dil se shukriya bc randirona sunne ke liye.. Bc tu nahi hota toh kya hota.. Main main keywords toh tune daal diye. Agar sab keywords daalne baithe toh bhi bhar jaega ye yearbook. Phir bhi dekhte hai..
Gadhi pe hasna, tera oyozone hona, TA ki gand maarna, meri tatti kismat pe rona, paper se pehle sath me hagna, tere bhand hone ke baad baate sunna, Hall 7 toh nahi bhulunga bhai, First year me Pandey ko pareshan karna, OAT ‚ù§Ô∏è, mujhe ulti karake sulane ke liye thanks, mera rr roz sunna, kattar hindu banna (Jai Shree Ram), Pankaj ke maze lena, din bhar tere room me pade rehna, bhai summer kaise bhul gaya tu, kaise pada rehta tha mai tere room me ü§£, roz 12 baje tujhe canteen bulana, Rishab tu aur mai bakchodi karna, tere aur Rishab ke jhagde aur usme mai aag lagata tha ü§£, gandu ek aur bhul gaya tu - Phy103 ke paper ke ek raat pehle library me bakchodi karna, 8-10 bhaiyo pe hasna, MOS dono baar (A ya B toh lag hi jaega madarchod ü§£), class bunk karke ccd canteen jana, Das ki dukaan, tujhe pehli baar daaru pilana, tera bihari naam karan karna, aauga bolna, subah YJHD dekhna aur gaane me background dancer pe hasna...
Aur kitna kuch hai bsdk..
Aakhri ek saal toh isse jyada bakchodi karni hai, ab paisa bhi hoga üòå, pure 4 saal ki khunnas ek me nikal lenge.. Khulega campus bhai.. Bakchodiya baaki hai... College life meri itni bakchod huyi hai aur safal huyi hai toh uska main reason Tu aur Rishab ho.. Love you brother.

PS- Mujhe ab bhi yaad hai pehli baar kaise mile the.. Paki ke room pe tu nanga khada tha aur tab sirf apan dono the jinko Dani pasand thi.. Dani is lub ‚ù§Ô∏è
Tab ye expect nahi kiya tha apan aise dost banege..
(Unexpected friendships are the best ones)
Jaldi mil bsdk. Saal ke upar ho gaya!

text:
Hey Deepak. Roz tera yearbook page kholke baith jaata hu kyuki samajh hi nhi aata kab aur kaha se shuru karu mai. Socha aaj pehla attempt maar hi lu. Toh first draft samajh ke baksh dena :P.

Thanks for being at the receiving end of rants, cribs and everyday rr. Tune naa sirf har baar sunaa (voh bhi itni dheeraj ke saath), par apna valuable feedback diya and har bar mujhe calm down kiya. And most importantly, you were always there as a rock for me to fall and rely on. Tere bina toh mai DE courses katai clear nhi kar paata. Raat bhar padna aur phir exam se pehle mujhe padana aur mere doubts clear karna. You even took the blame for me for some of my fuckups in courses! I can't express how grateful I am to have you as a friend during my stay here.

You're the guy who made me fall into love with memes, wholesomeness, shayari, gazal, music and literature. Bhai maine tujhe kitni baar kaha hai, apni kavitao ko publish kar par tu sunta hi nhi -_-. Pata nhi kyu khud ki talent ki kadr hi nhi karta. Thank you for the daily dose of dopamine and serotonin via the memes and music you send my way on a daily basis. Sometimes that is all one needs to drag through their mundane day and life :). 

Keep on spreading happiness man. And ab jaate jaate apne time management ke raaz bhi batate jaa :P. Counselling, HSS, acads, memes aur pata nhi kya kay ek saath sambhal leta hai XO. Thanks for being such an integral part of my campus life.  Bas jald se noida aa phir chill karte apan saath mein :P. Wishing you all the best for your life ahead. And once again, Thank you! ^_^

text:
CCD at 7?
I am thankful to Pragya for many things, but making me meet you tops the list. I remember thinking in the very start- A* Allen, CSE damn he must be very studious. Skip to 4 years later, " Shreyash class ajaya kar kabhi" :p I have enjoyed a lottt with you, from our ccd hangouts to random strolls, and oh how can I forget the trip-why was I so rude to you lol. You've been my partner in crime in pretty much everything but I hate you for not texting me often, you better work on that. We should have made a reel together yar, but I hope we meet soon someday and then pakka we'll make a reel that matches your level of cringe ok :p We rarely talk about emotional stuff but I'll use this opportunity to say, thank you. You have been there for me (knowingly or unknowingly ) in some of my most sad times and you always managed to cheer me up. Will always remember the Abhishek Upmanyu show and the time we spend in Liquid after that, one of the best nights in those 4 years
I wish you all the luck to survive one more year of college without me :p
Miss you a lot, Love you <3

text:
The coronavirus variant discovered in South Africa can break through the protection provided by Pfizer Inc and BioNTech's COVID-19 vaccine to some extent, a real-world data study in Israel found. However, the variant's prevalence in Israel is very low and the vaccine remains highly effective.

The study was released on the medRxiv pre-print site on April 9 and has not been peer reviewed. It compared almost 400 people who had tested positive for COVID-19, after they received one or two doses of the vaccine, against the same number of unvaccinated patients with the disease.

It matched age and gender, among other characteristics.

The South African variant, B.1.351, was found to make up about 1% of all the COVID-19 cases across all the people studied, according to the study by Tel Aviv University and Israel's largest healthcare provider, Clalit.

But among patients who had received two doses of the vaccine, the variant's prevalence rate was eight times higher than those unvaccinated - 5.4% versus 0.7%.

This suggests the vaccine is less effective against the South African variant, compared with the original coronavirus and a variant first identified in Britain that has come to comprise nearly all COVID-19 cases in Israel, the researchers said.

The researchers said the study was not intended to assess overall vaccine effectiveness against any variant, since it only looked at people who had already tested positive for COVID-19, not at overall infection rates.

Separate real-world Israeli studies on the vaccine's overall effectiveness, including by Clalit, have shown the Pfizer shot to be more than 90% effective. L1N2KU3L6

"We found a disproportionately higher rate of the South African variant among people vaccinated with a second dose, compared to the unvaccinated group. This means that the South African variant is able, to some extent, to break through the vaccine's protection," said Tel Aviv University's Adi Stern.

In an update to the study posted on April 16, the researchers noted that within the group of people who received two doses, which comprised eight people, all of the B.1.351 infections occurred within a week to 13 days after the second shot. None of them tested positive for it 14 days or more after the second dose.

text: I borrowed this one from work, and, afraid of doing damage to its white binding, I bought a cloth cover, originally no doubt intended for bibles, to protect the book from smudges or anything else untoward. That covering became symbolic as I dived into this memoir of hiding, transformation, and reversals. In the Darkroom follows feminist scholar Susan Faludi as she reunites with her estranged father, who is now living as a woman in the Budapest of her youth. Her father survived the Holocaust through disguises and subterfuge, then found refuge after the war in depictions of women on film; she is proud to show her daughter the life she has made in Budapest, even as right wing nationalism grows around her. Susan Faludi frankly discusses her struggle to accept her father, both in her estrangement and in her new life as woman, and reading the memoir of an old school feminist figure out how to be trans-inclusive is one of the most heartwarming things you‚Äôll ever come across.
author: Sajal  Chaurasia

author: Siddharth  Jayashankar

text:
I am sure everyone knows how hardworking you are, how intelligent you are and yada yada yada (who the f**k doesn't ever get even close to getting a B what the f**k man!).

I still remember the first memory I have of you was the first year when the Prof was trying to derive some detailed result, and midway in his second page he gets stuck. After few minutes of utter silence and confusion, I one guy (out of the odd 400) pointing out that he did a small error somewhere in the first page (!!) of the proof. The image I had of you then is the same I have of you know. Super focused and Super confident.

I think we got to know each other better from the third-semester thermodynamics and in the time we spent together, I have come to know that you are one of the most helpful and honest guys I have ever met (and probably will meet). Sounds cliche? But people often underestimate the importance of being honest to yourself and others in terms of having a long-term friendship. That is something I will take with me forever.

This memoir can't encapsulate how grateful I am for getting me through this undergrad (special mention to that horrible "apping" season of 2019-2020). I would never really understand why you chose to be friends with me, help and guide me in almost all walks of life, and share my love for food and music. 

Although we didn't get the chance to invade our beloved base in the 8th semester (I was anyways planning not to be around in my 7th), you have always been a text away, ready to help/offer your honest criticism. I hope we stay that way forever. Now I know, this won't change anything but please please please please please decide against the K-word we are not allowed to speak about.

Cheers to good times, that were and that will be.
author: Snehal  Raj

text:
Expect toh nahi kar rahe hoge aage jo kuch bhi likhne wala hu mai, but padh lo (pata nahi fir likhunga ya nahi)

Campus me mera aur tumhara passive-aggressive relation is the most fun relation I have had. Kisi bhi din, kisi bhi samay, bas tumhare room jaake baith jao and kaafi maza aata tha. It just happens that even without trying you can crack jokes out of thin air by judging people, exposing unspoken customs and just using that sharp brain of yours to make super weird connections. Jab bhi room ghuso, hamesha lete rahoge, mobile dekhte rahoge aur agar exams paas aa rahe ho toh padhte rahoge.  Mai aur tum khaane ka interest bhi share karte the and canteen me numerous times saath me khaya hai humne. 

 First year me toh almost saare  and second year ke kuch courses saath me discuss karte the and Vipul Arora (fraud) internship bhi saath me hi kara tha. In general jo bhi courses tumhare saath kiya hai, usse yeh toh keh sakta hu bohot tez ho bhai tum. Mai ek mahina padh ke bhi jitne number nahi laa sakta, tum bc ek raat me nikal lete ho. People might think that you start studying late, but I would say that you start studying at the exact time that is needed. Ek week pehle se tumhara fatna chalu ho jaata hai and uss last week me jo kuch kar lete ho tum, that shows that you can adapt in any situation and are fucking intelligent.  I am sure you will excel a lot (I say this for very few people).

All our fights and dissing aside, you have always been very helpful and you have always respected me (more than I deserved). Bilkul bhi fake nahi karte apne aap ko and  apna mazaak udane se bhi piche nahi hat te. Tumhare saath rehke maza toh kaafi aata hai. I know you are driven highly by achieving success and kisi bhi cheez me dimaag laga doge toh achieve toh kar hi loge. 

In future, I will always be ready to help in whatever way I can and would love to keep in touch. Machate toh tum rahoge hi, bas apna confidence level thoda badhao aur woh tatti clash of clans khelna band karo.

Cheers Shubham

I saw you first time on 22nd July 2017, obviously the first day of IITK. We were in the same cab, And your unique voice can be recognized even in the crowded auditorium of 830 students.
Shuruaat me to koi baat hi nahi hui.. and 3rd year me saath me project mila, you have a dominating nature at that time, jesse tum baat baat par bolti thi ki "Tumse bola tha karne ko to kyu nahi kiya" and kaafi daata tumne uss project me mujhe. 
uske ek saal baad firse project partner ban gaye..üòÇüòÇ coincidentally... iss baar mujhe lag raha tha ki daant to nahi khaani tumhari.. to saara kaam kar diya time se..
CHE352 ke baad socha nahi tha kabhi itne ache dost ban paayenge..

"Maybe you have to know the darkness before you can appreciate the light." and you are much "brighter" and way more mature than I think earlier.

text: Bhai apani baatein most probably intern se hi chalu hui. Bhot kuch seekha terese iss span mein. Tu nhi hota toh shyd hum dono ko bhot problems aati. Yaad hai time-series wla task mereko diya tha ifti ne aur merese ho nhi rha tha maine tereko bola aur tune poora 2 din mein akele kr dia tha aur resluts bhi imporve kr diye the. I know tu bhot hi simple, helpful aur thoda shy nature ka hai. Pr bhai bhot jyda talented hai tu, pehle bs suna tha but summer mein dekh bhi liya. Keep up themhard work, kabhi future mein kabhi tere saath kaam krne ka mauka mila toh bhot acha lgega. Apan kabhi mil nhi paaye, kaash muaka mile. All the best bhai for your future endeavours!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: Bhai kahan se shuru krun. Tereko shyd yaad na ho , pehli baar tu mila tha jb tu E-Cell ke event ke liye sbko bulane aaya tha. Phir ek do br tere room pe mila, kya safai rkhta tha bhai tu. First summers se toh bhai saath  hi rhe. Woh summer kya epic tha. Mai bahar jyada nhi jta tha, isliye saath bhot photos nhi hai yr, but memories bhot hein. Hr course se related itni hein ki kya btaun. Baswana sir wla toh yaad hi hoga.OS yaad hai tu roj uthane aata tha aur hum soe reh jte the.  Last year maien socha tha yr ghumenge pr kya hi ho gya. Phir bhi last mein tum logon ne saare mze krwa hi diye. Bhot ache din the yr, yeah akhiri ke 1-2 mahine campus mein.  Ek GOA trip krni hai bhai saath mein, jb bhi time mile. Tere aur tere bhai mein pehchana mushkil h bhai. Jld hi milte hein yr.  All the best!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: Vijju boi!!! Bhai first year mein french kiss ki kahaniya sunate the tum.Aapki woh delhi ki sad story hume abhi tk yaad hai. Phir apna killer dance hua ><, aapki wajah se codechef pr coding krni chalu ki. Aapka CS aur NLP ka pyar kabhi km na ho.Thoda guilt reh gya yr jyada time sath nhi bita pye, shyd saara time mera assignment aur rone mein hi nikal jta tha. But apni bhot saari cheezon pr vibes match  krti hein, aage apan jrur connect mein rhenge. Tumhare aur shashank ke common "interests" hmesha yaad rhenge, woh SIS ke saath bakchodiyan, raat ko terrace pe antakshari aur dumbsharads. Tere 2 hi modes hein, ya toh din br CSGo ya phir din bhar kaam(continuous itna kaise baith lete ho bhai). Pr aakhiri do mahino min bhot kuch jaana tere baare mein. Aur haan us din jb tu high tha kuch nhi bola tha bhai, dra mt kr. Kafi weight loss kr lia tune, aise hi gym aur protein shake mein lga reh.  Aur haan bhai bina imposter bne mereko vent kyun krwa deta h? Bs aise hi chaapta reh aur haan tere paper ki treat abhi tk bachi hai . All the Best Bhai!!!
author: Ritesh  Kumar

text: Hello Anshu Dada. Bhai yaar.... saal bhar ho gaya mile. Ummid hai ki tum aage bhi life me time to time gyan dete rahoge aise hiüòú. Or bhai bohot gussa aata tha jab tu mujhe jabardasti hockey ke liye uthake leke jaata tha... sona bhi jaruri hota hai yaar.... Par bohot bohot dhanyabad aise baar baar uthane ke liye kyuki Hokey IITK me meri life ke best parts me se ek thi or uski existence me tera kafi bada haath hai. Mene tere muh se kabhi ye nhi suna ki me thak gaya bhagte bhagteüòÇ. Life me bss tere jitna stamina chahiye, meri to 2 km me hi haalat patli ho jati hai or tu 20 minute me 6KM bhag leta tha. Apna enthu aise hi high rakhna balak. Baki yaade to or bhi banti rahegi abhi saari zandgi padi hai. Or dobara hockey khelne chalna ho to bata dena... jabardasti nhi karni padegi, chal chalega me aise hi. Or ye Prateek se bol de ki muh sambhal ke baat kare... kuch bhi bolta hai yaar, matlab thik hai yaar tum dono Kanpur ke ho, samjh sakta hu me, par iska matlab ye thodi hai ki mujhe sideline karo dono milke?

text:
Anshuman bhaiiiiii!
yar tum logo ki vajah se hi mai ab jyada introvert nhi hu, kya bnda hai be tu, bohot maze kiye apan ne yr, agla udghosh hota to mai pakka khud bnda head aur tereko jabardasti banwata.
Bhai calling krna bandiyo ko, race lagana kaun jyada call kr skta xD, kya hi bakchodiya hui thi udghosh me, pankaj ka call krna, fir bhag jana chupchap room se haha, aur sale tum photoshoot me nhi aaya tha udghosh wali, fir akhri ke 2 month me bhi, sale mila hi nhi, antaragni me bhi bhag gya tha spardha nhi to mst tadte idhar.
Aur ha akhe shambhal ke tada kr bhai, haha, hawsi lgta pura xD, aur tune usko baja diya na? samaz rha na kiske liye bol rha?
Bhai, Udghosh ki vajah se itna accha dost mila mereko kabhi socha nhi tha, bhai bohot load tha hospi ka sahi me, khaskar types ki cancelling ke baad, pr kisi tarah nipat gya hehe, akhir raat me apan ne khub maze kiye, fir sale tu hockey khelne nikal gya. Last din yaad hai? ham dono literally pade the GnS room me, itne thak gye the, bandiya aayi, tu itna jaldi utha xD, aur BHU wali pasand thi na tujhe baat kr usse, bohot memories banayi bhai.
Milte rehna nhi bolunga kyuki tu milega pakka, kanpur ka hi jo hai,Aur bhai placement ki treat lena baki hai terese, aur pankaj se bhi party leni hai to milte hai puri team aur bakchodiya kat-te, I can say ki IITK ka one of the closest-friend hai tu, jisse mai saari baate share kr skta. All the best bhaiii for future, will cheer you up.
